    "In Nawang et al (2021) systematic literature review, the authors discussed the use of the EDM, LA, and ML to predict student's academic performance in secondary schools and higher educational institutions.",
    "This review provided an overview of the methods and algorithms that are used in the prediction and identified the features that have the most significant effects on their performance.",
    "It mentioned that the academic feature category outperforms other feature categories, and is where the majority of features are utilized when predicting student's performance.",
    "Another finding from this review is that, in comparison to academic performance, GPA, exam scores, and marks are the best indicators of performance.",
